{"tid":831363,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞媒體諷刺C.朗：離開皇馬球證就不幫你","createTime":"2018-09-22T01:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T06:12:46.000Z","uid":147522,"like":56,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2d845268e29d50d44fbdc6f7cfb6a817df48739e","tid":831363,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:34:43.000Z","msg":"C.朗拿度的紅牌是本週國際球壇最具話題性的事件，親巴塞的加泰羅尼亞媒體習慣性的發聲，對C.朗拿度進行嘲諷。<br />\n<br />\n　　《世界體育報》的大標題是「C.朗拿度領到紅牌，他喊住離場」，文章寫道：「他與穆里洛糾纏在一起，然後領到紅牌，又喊到好似小朋友一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n　　《世界體育報》還嘲諷說，C.朗拿度之前靠著球證保護多次逃脫，現在離開了有球證罩著的皇馬，他便受到了懲罰。「之前在效力葡萄牙和皇馬時，C.朗拿度有20次明顯的暴力行徑逃過處罰，如今代表祖記的歐冠盃第一場比賽，他終於被罰下了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「這證明了，離開了馬德里和皇馬，球證們的保護不復存在了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　在意大利，媒體多站在C.朗拿度這邊，譴責球證過於嚴厲的判罰。《都靈體育報》稱，這張紅牌「荒唐」、是個「醜聞」。"},{"pid":"0e7cd0949713ba7a037d6e3e99a2f809fe2f3c16","tid":831363,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda34784047b5e0e016de4e18e0e5632a9e5bfc6","tid":831363,"uid":99700,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"祖記d錢拎哂去買c朗 冇錢收買球證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00aec00f9b1fa44732f65bf7d967eb32da02c1b2","tid":831363,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843ffa04fef57e44791cf27be6bb47e774b2a2be","tid":831363,"uid":1977,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:38:30.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6852e74cc4c9cf32247fc2223fb899004470c10","tid":831363,"uid":195627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acb1b